name: The Carlton Dining Table
description: A round dining table fusing Art Deco style with contemporary elegance, the Carlton oozes style and would also work excellently as a centre table at the smaller size. The circular top boasts a stunning radial pattern with a beautiful ripple grain movement, all standing on a graceful cured shaped pedestal on a smooth facetted base. This pedestal round dining table is available in any of Davidson's luxury wood and lacquer finishes in a range of different shades, with a gleaming metal collar and band that runs sleekly around the base. The Carlton dining table would bring beauty to any dining room or hallway, when used as a centre piece, and promises to enhance a special dining experience.
